sources.title: Fraidy Cat CARTOON HOUR
sources.description:
This Fraidy Cat cartoon Special includes (1) Magic Numbers, (2) Choo-Choo Fraidy, (3) Lollipop Burglar, (4) Cupid the Cat, (4) Feline Fortune, (5) Love is a Many Feathered Thing, (6) Meaner Than a Junkyard Cat, (7) Over the Wall Having a Ball, (8) This Cat for Hire, (9) The Not so Nice Mice.  

Unlucky cat, “Fraidy,” has used up eight of his nine lives, but even worse, if he accidentally says a number from 1 to 8 (or sound-a-like words) a ghost from that life returns to haunt him! This 1975 cartoon show originally appeared as a segment on Filmation's short-lived ABC series Uncle Croc's Block.
